asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Ratchet
description:
This Fluf is a master with his hands. Matter of fact, he can fix practically anything.
A former student assistant to Professor Sparky, Ratchet learned everything he could about robotics, mechanics and engineering. He even helped the professor create the robo thingies, and as a result he now has one of his own, a creative little eight legged friend named Clank.
Now that Ratchet is no longer studying under Professor Sparky, he spends his days doing handyfluf jobs in the burrows, working on jetpacks, hoverboards, and anything that needs fixing in Fluf World and the metaverse beyond.
But Ratchet isn’t all work and no play, by night he loves to chew on mycelium and party it up with his fellow flufs. His glow stick necklace is for more than just raving, it also helps light up anything he’s working on, and acts as a beacon to attract female attention when partying it up in the burrows.
Ratchet has a deep longing to be out amongst the stars. He has a slight recollection that he’s been out there before. . . before the wreck. . . But that’s as much as he can remember now.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: Pouncer
description:
For every great Mr Fluf, there’s an even greater Mrs Fluf. 

Pouncer isn’t just your ordinary female, she’s a gal that gets **** done. A self-sufficient woman who doesn’t mind getting her burrow dirty. Her fur is a reflection of her personality, although she looks innocent she’s feisty and always ready to Pounce... 

The Fluffle is her world and without her, there will be no more Flufs... she’s always wanted her own family of little Fluffetts so when the right size carrot presents itself she might just invite him down the rabbit hole for a little nibble...

name: Doctor Stamets
description: Space is cold, and I have been searching this universe for eons trying to understand the mycelial network.  The spore drive of my space ship allows for space folding. I simply connect my ear to the network and as long as I have enough energy, I can guide us in an instant to any part of the meta verse. I am at the forefront of space exploration and research. I always say, one can never be too over dressed for that chance encounter, so love to keep my fur shimmering and wear my favourite gold bow tie. I have been through many black holes, crossed dimensions and galaxies. Still searching for my mate and bringing the meta verse together. Will we find new worlds, will we find new friends and mates. Come join me, follow this shimmering white rabbit down another hole.

asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Raoul Duke
description: We were somewhere around Barstow on the edge of the desert when the drugs began to take hold. I remember saying something like I feel a bit lightheaded maybe you should drive. And suddenly there was a terrible roar all around us and the sky was full of what looked like huge bats, all swooping and screeching and diving around the car, which was going about a hundred miles an hour with the top down to Las Vegas. And a voice was screaming Holy Jesus! What are these **** animals? Then it was quiet again. My attorney had taken his shirt off and was pouring beer on his chest, to facilitate the tanning process. What the hell are you yelling about? he muttered, staring up at the sun with his eyes closed and covered with wraparound Spanish sunglasses. Never mind, I said. Its your turn to drive.
